ChatGPT is like a very smart computer program that can write things on its own. If you give it a short sentence or a few words, it can continue writing from there and create a whole paragraph or even a story. But it doesn't always write the same thing, it can give you different stories or paragraphs each time you give it the same starting sentence or words. So, it's like a game where you write the first part and then the computer writes the rest.